lopment of web applications\",\n          \"Wrote unit tests\",\n          \"Participated in code reviews\"\n        ]\n      }\n    ],\n    \"education\": {\n      \"degree\": \"Bachelor of Science in Computer Science\",\n      \"university\": \"University of California, Berkeley\",\n      \"graduation_date\": \"2018\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"match_indicators\": {\n    \"required_skills_total\": 7,\n    \"required_skills_matched\": 5,\n    \"required_skill_match_ratio\": 0.71,\n    \"preferred_skills_total\": 4,\n    \"preferred_skills_matched\": 2,\n    \"preferred_skill_match_ratio\": 0.50,\n    \"experience_level_match\": true,\n    \"education_match\": true,\n    \"overall_match_score\": 0.78,\n    \"responsibility_keywords_matched\": 7\n  },\n  \"extracted_features\": {\n    \"programming_languages\": [\"Python\", \"SQL\"],\n    \"data_structures\": [\"Data Structures\"],\n    \"algorithms\": [\"Algorithms\"],\n    \"object_oriented_programming\": [\"Object-Oriented Programming\"],\n    \"databases\": [\"SQL\"],\n    \"cloud_platforms\": [\"AWS\"],\n    \"machine_learning\": [\"Machine Learning\"],\n    \"methodologies\": [\"Agile (inferred)\", \"DevOps (inferred)\"],\n    \"soft_skills\": [\"Communication\", \"Teamwork\"],\n    \"tools_and_frameworks\": []\n  }\n}\n```"}
{"timestamp": "2026-05-26 17:26:16,941", "level": "INFO", "logger": "flow.execution", "module": "flow", "function": "run_async", "line": 205, "message": " - task1: ```json\n{\n  \"technical_questions\": [\n    {\n      \"question\": \"Describe your experience with Python. Can you provide an example of a challenging project where you used Python and the specific libraries or frameworks you utilized?\",\n      \"follow_up_questions\": [\n        \"How did you handle performance optimization in that project?\",\n        \"What testing strategies did you employ?\",\n        \"How did you manage dependencies?\"\n      ],\n      \"category\": \"Programming Languages\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"question\": \"Explain your understanding of Data Structures and Algorithms. Can you describe a situation where you had to choose a specific data structure or algorithm to optimize performance? What factors influenced your decision?\",\n      \"follow_up_questions\": [\n        \"What was the time complexity of your solution?\",\n        \"How did you validate the performance improvements?\",\n        \"Are there any trade-offs to your chosen approach?\"\n      ],\n      \"category\": \"Data Structures & Algorithms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"question\": \"Discuss your experience with Object-Oriented Programming principles. How have you applied these principles in your previous projects to improve code maintainability and scalability?\",\n      \"follow_up_questions\": [\n        \"Can you give an example of using inheritance or polymorphism?\",\n        \"How do you ensure your classes are loosely coupled?\",\n        \"What design patterns are you familiar with?\"\n      ],\n      \"category\": \"Object-Oriented Programming\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"question\": \"Describe your experience with database management, specifically using SQL. Can you walk me through a complex SQL query you've written and explain how you optimized it for performance?\",\n      \"follow_up_questions\": [\n        \"What indexing strategies did you use?\",\n        \"How did you handle large datasets?\",\n        \"What database systems have you worked with?\"\n      ],\n      \"category\": \"Databases\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"question\": \"Explain your experience with AWS. Can you describe a project where you utilized AWS services? Which services did you use, and what were the benefits of using AWS in that context?\",\n      \"follow_up_questions\": [\n        \"How did you handle security in your AWS environment?\",\n        \"What strategies did you use for cost optimization?\",\n        \"How did you automate deployment and scaling?\"\n      ],\n      \"category\": \"Cloud Platforms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"question\": \"Describe your experience with Machine Learning. What types of machine learning algorithms have you worked with, and how did you evaluate their performance? Please provide a specific example.\",\n      \"follow_up_questions\": [\n        \"How did you handle data preprocessing?\",\n        \"What metrics did you use to evaluate your model?\",\n        \"How did you address overfitting?\"\n      ],\n      \"category\": \"Machine Learning\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"behavioral_questions\": [\n    {\n      \"question\": \"Describe a situation where you had to work in a team to solve a complex problem. What was your role, and how did you contribute to the team's success?\",\n      \"follow_up_questions\": [\n        \"How did you handle disagreements within the team?\",\n        \"What did you learn from the experience?\",\n        \"How did you ensure effective communication?\"\n      ],\n      \"category\": \"Teamwork\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"question\": \"Tell me about a time when you had to deal with a tight deadline or unexpected obstacle while working on a project. How did you handle the situation, and what was the outcome?\",\n      \"follow_up_questions\": [\n        \"How did you prioritize tasks?\",\n        \"Did you ask for help? If so, from whom?\",\n        \"What would you do differently next time?\"\n      ],\n      \"category\": \"Problem Solving\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"question\": \"Describe a time when you had to explain a technical concept to a non-technical audience. How did you ensure they understood the information?\",\n      \"follow_up_questions\": [\n        \"What strategies did you use to simplify the explanation?\",\n        \"How did you gauge their understanding?\",\n        \"What was the result of the communication?\"\n      ],\n      \"category\": \"Communication\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"question\": \"Give an example of a time you took initiative on a project. What motivated you to do so, and what was the result?\",\n      \"follow_up_questions\": [\n        \"How did you identify the need for initiative?\",\n        \"What obstacles did you face?\",\n        \"How did your initiative benefit the project or team?\"\n      ],\n      \"category\": \"Initiative\"\n    },\n    {\n       \"question\": \"Tell me about a time you received negative feedback. How did you respond?\",\n       \"follow_up_questions\": [\n         \"How did you process it?\",\n         \"What steps did you take?\",\n         \"What did you learn?\"\n       ],\n       \"category\": \"Feedback\"\n     }\n  ]\n}\n```"}
{"timestamp": "2026-05-26 17:26:16,941", "level": "INFO", "logger": "flow.execution", "module": "flow", "function": "run_async", "line": 205, "message": " - task2: ```json\n{\n  \"interview_session\": {\n    \"candidate_name\": \"John Doe\",\n    \"job_title\": \"Software Engineer\",\n    \"date\": \"2024-01-01\",\n    \"interviewer\": \"Recruiter Name\",\n    \"sections\": [\n      {\n        \"section_name\": \"Technical Assessment\",\n        \"questions\": [\n          {\n            \"question_id\": \"T1\",\n            \"question_text\": \"Describe your experience with Python. Can you provide an example of a challenging project where you used Python and the specific libraries or frameworks you utilized?\",\n            \"candidate_response\": \"The candidate described a project involving data analysis where they used Pandas and Scikit-learn. They discussed the challenges of handling large datasets and optimizing performance.\",\n            \"follow_up_questions\": [\n              {\n                \"follow_up_id\": \"T1.1\",\n                \"follow_up_text\": \"How did you handle performance optimization in that project?\",\n                \"candidate_response\": \"The candidate explained their use of vectorization and efficient data structures to improve processing speed.\"\n              },\n              {\n                \"follow_up_id\": \"T1.2\",\n                \"follow_up_text\": \"What testing strategies did you employ?\",\n                \"candidate_response\": \"The candidate discussed using unit tests and integration tests to ensure code quality.\"\n              }\n            ]\n          },\n          {\n            \"question_id\": \"T2\",\n            \"question_text\": \"Explain your understanding of Data Structures and Algorithms. Can you describe a situation where you had to choose a specific data structure or algorithm to optimize performance? What factors influenced your decision?\",\n            \"candidate_response\": \"The candidate described a scenario where they used a hash map to optimize search operations in a large dataset. They explained the trade-offs between time and space complexity.\",\n            \"follow_up_questions\": [\n              {\n                \"follow_up_id\": \"T2.1\",\n                \"follow_up_text\": \"What was the time complexity of your solution?\",\n                \"candidate_response\": \"The candidate stated the time complexity was O(1) on average for search operations.\"\n              },\n              {\n                \"follow_up_id\": \"T2.2\",\n                \"follow_up_text\": \"How did you validate the performance improvements?\",\n                \"candidate_response\": \"The candidate mentioned using benchmarking tools to measure the execution time before and after the optimization.\"\n              }\n            ]\n          },\n          {\n            \"question_id\": \"T3\",\n            \"question_text\": \"Discuss your experience with Object-Oriented Programming principles. How have you applied these principles in your previous projects to improve code maintainability and scalability?\",\n            \"candidate_response\": \"The candidate explained their understanding of encapsulation, inheritance, and polymorphism, and provided examples of how they used these principles to create modular and reusable code.\",\n            \"follow_up_questions\": [\n              {\n                \"follow_up_id\": \"T3.1\",\n                \"follow_up_text\": \"Can you give an example of using inheritance or polymorphism?\",\n                \"candidate_response\": \"The candidate gave example of using inheritance to implement different types of data processors.\"\n              }\n            ]\n          },\n          {\n            \"question_id\": \"T4\",\n            \"question_text\": \"Describe your experience with database management, specifically using SQL. Can you walk me through a complex SQL query you've written and explain how you optimized it for performance?\",\n            \"candidate_response\": \"The candidate detailed experience in query optimization, using indexes, and writing stored procedures. They gave an example of a complex query used to generate reports.\",\n            \"follow_up_questions\": [\n              {\n                \"follow_up_id\": \"T4.1\",\n                \"follow_up_text\": \"What indexing strategies did you use?\",\n                \"candidate_response\": \"The candidate mentioned using clustered and non-clustered indexes based on the query patterns.\"\n              }\n            ]\n          },\n          {\n            \"question_id\": \"T5\",\n            \"question_text\": \"Explain your experience with AWS. Can you describe a project where you utilized AWS services? Which services did you use, and what were the benefits of using AWS in that context?\",\n            \"candidate_response\": \"The candidate described a project where they used EC2 for compute, S3 for storage, and Lambda for serverless functions. They mentioned the benefits of scalability and cost-effectiveness.\",\n            \"follow_up_questions\": [\n              {\n                \"follow_up_id\": \"T5.1\",\n                \"follow_up_text\": \"How did you handle security in your AWS environment?\",\n                \"candidate_response\": \"The candidate described using IAM roles and security groups to control access to AWS resources.\"\n              }\n            ]\n          },\n                   {\n            \"question_id\": \"T6\",\n            \"question_text\": \"Describe your experience with Machine Learning. What types of machine learning algorithms have you worked with, and how did you evaluate their performance? Please provide a specific example.\",\n            \"candidate_response\": \"The candidate detailed experience with linear regression, logistic regression, and support vector machines. They described a project with model building and evaluation.\",\n            \"follow_up_questions\": [\n              {\n                \"follow_up_id\": \"T6.1\",\n                \"follow_up_text\": \"How did you handle data preprocessing?\",\n                \"candidate_response\": \"The candidate mentioned techniques of normalization and feature scaling.\"\n              }\n            ]\n          }\n        ]\n      },\n      {\n        \"section_name\": \"Behavioral Assessment\",\n        \"questions\": [\n          {\n            \"question_id\": \"B1\",\n            \"question_text\": \"Describe a situation where you had to work in a team to solve a complex problem. What was your role, and how did you contribute to the team's success?\",\n            \"candidate_response\": \"The candidate described a project where they worked with a cross-functional team to develop a new feature for a web application. They highlighted their role in designing and implementing the user interface.\",\n            \"follow_up_questions\": [\n              {\n                \"follow_up_id\": \"B1.1\",\n                \"follow_up_text\": \"How did you handle disagreements within the team?\",\n                \"candidate_response\": \"The candidate stated they encourage all members to voice concerns.\"\n              }\n            ]\n          },\n          {\n            \"question_id\": \"B2\",\n            \"question_text\": \"Tell me about a time when you had to deal with a tight deadline or unexpected obstacle while working on a project. How did you handle the situation, and what was the outcome?\",\n            \"candidate_response\": \"The candidate recounted a situation where a critical database server failed just before a major product launch. They described their efforts to quickly diagnose the problem and implement a workaround.\",\n            \"follow_up_questions\": [\n              {\n                \"follow_up_id\": \"B2.1\",\n                \"follow_up_text\": \"How did you prioritize tasks?\",\n                \"candidate_response\": \"The candidate prioritized the critical tasks.\"\n              }\n            ]\n          },\n          {\n            \"question_id\": \"B3\",\n            \"question_text\": \"Describe a time when you had to explain a technical concept to a non-technical audience. How did you ensure they understood the information?\",\n            \"candidate_response\": \"The candidate described a time when they had to explain the benefits of a new software system to a group of business stakeholders. They focused on using clear and concise language and avoiding technical jargon.\",\n            \"follow_up_questions\": [\n              {\n                \"follow_up_id\": \"B3.1\",\n                \"follow_up_text\": \"What strategies did you use to simplify the explanation?\",\n                \"candidate_response\": \"The candidate mentioned using analogies and real-world examples to illustrate the concepts.\"\n              }\n            ]\n          },\n          {\n            \"question_id\": \"B4\",\n            \"question_text\": \"Give an example of a time you took initiative on a project. What motivated you to do so, and what was the result?\",\n            \"candidate_response\": \"The candidate recalled implementing a new code review process.\",\n            \"follow_up_questions\": [\n              {\n                \"follow_up_id\": \"B4.1\",\n                \"follow_up_text\": \"How did you identify the need for initiative?\",\n                \"candidate_response\": \"The candidate noticed increasing bug reports.\"\n              }\n            ]\n          },\n          {\n            \"question_id\": \"B5\",\n            \"question_text\": \"Tell me about a time you received negative feedback. How did you respond?\",\n            \"candidate_response\": \"The candidate shared receiving feedback about documentation.\",\n            \"follow_up_questions\": [\n              {\n                \"follow_up_id\": \"B5.1\",\n                \"follow_up_text\": \"How did you process it?\",\n                \"candidate_response\": \"The candidate reevaluated their strategy.\"\n              }\n            ]\n          }\n        ]\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}\n```"}
