ence and insights with us.\\n\\n[Option A: Positive Follow-up] The team was very impressed with your background and skills. We are currently in the process of considering all candidates and will be in touch within [Timeframe] with an update on the next steps.\\n\\n[Option B: Request for Additional Information] To assist us in our evaluation, we would appreciate it if you could provide [Specific Information Requested - e.g., references, code samples, project details] by [Date].\\n\\n[Option C: Negative Follow-up (Rejection)] After careful consideration, we have decided to move forward with other candidates whose qualifications and experience more closely align with the requirements of this role. We appreciate your interest in [Company Name] and encourage you to apply for other suitable positions in the future.\\n\\nThank you again for your time.\\n\\nSincerely,\\n[Your Name]\\n[Your Title]\\n[Company Name]\\n[Contact Information]\",\n    \"placeholders\": {\n      \"Company Name\": \"[Company Name - e.g., Tech Solutions Inc.]\",\n      \"Date\": \"[Date - e.g., October 26, 2023]\",\n      \"Timeframe\": \"[Timeframe - e.g., one week]\",\n      \"Specific Information Requested\": \"[Specific Information Requested - e.g., references, code samples, project details]\",\n      \"Your Name\": \"[Recruiter Name]\",\n      \"Your Title\": \"[Recruiter Title]\",\n      \"Contact Information\": \"[Recruiter Contact Information - e.g., email and phone number]\"\n    },\n    \"options\": [\n      \"Positive Follow-up\",\n      \"Request for Additional Information\",\n      \"Negative Follow-up (Rejection)\"\n    ]\n  }\n}\n```"}
